summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $4.62, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the general fund of the City of Seattle, to pay the general taxes for 1905 and 1909, on part of lot 30, block 1, Aabling 1st Addition; part of lots 1 to 11, inclusive, and lot 22, block 1, Banner Tracts to West Seattle, and a part of lot 38, block 11, Ballard Park Addition.
